<h1 id="iii">III</h1>

<p>What was the one true thing:</p>
<ul>
  <li>English culture still has a colonial-class like precedence over Indian culture. Rowling, EPL and WWE - Guitar, not Sitar. Krishna and Mahabharat - they were interested in Gandalf and The Battle of Minas Tirith</li>
  <li>Rich kids care about sports, power, and arts.</li>
